# Title: SugusGuardGAB General Apple Blocklist
# Description: SugusGuard's Apple filterlist for AdGuard Home / AdGuard Pro App
# Description: Be warned: This will brick some - for us anyway unnecessary - functions
# List-URL: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SugusGuard/Blocklists/main/SugusGuardGAB
#
## Prevent filter-bypassing with https requests as Apple like to do
#
!||*^$dnstype=HTTPS,dnsrewrite=REFUSED;;,important
||use-application-dns.net^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED;;,important
#
## Whitelist
#
! Nothing whitelisted yet
#
